<P>
   PRAYER-HEALING _ Do you bring the power of prayer into the
operating room? Yes, say many doctors and their patients who
discuss how they believe spirituality made the physical healing
better..trying to get with Braves Andres Gallaraga, who swears his
winning streak is due to prayer teamed with his surgery. Also
includes a box of how to approach your physician about praying
together or other spiritual matters if important to you. (Lore,
