reformed segregationist will face off against black businessman
James Perkins, the man he beat out the last time in a mayoralty
election many suspect was tainted. By Marcella Bombardieri. 1460
words.
</P>
<P>
   NAPSTER-COLLEGES (Undated) _ Many colleges are blocking access
to Napster, the music download web site, in dorms and computer labs
this fall, irritating devotees of the service. But bans could
become the trend: A lawyer for Metallica and Dr. Dre has asked 11
top universities to block Napster on their systems. By Patrick
Healy. 1090 words.
</P>
