   BOOK-TIPS (Undated) _ What's hot on the just-published list.
</P>
<P>
   MUSIC-FALL-CDS (Undated) _ Whether you're a troubled soul who
swoons to the dark musings of PJ Harvey or the good-natured type
who prefers your ear candy light as air a la Barenaked Ladies, it's
going to be a blockbuster fall for pop and rock CDs. By Joan
Anderman. 1150 words.
</P>
