<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-09-11 16:18 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A9078 &Cx1f; tab-z
r a BC-ECOM-ALLIANCES-NYTSF &LR;      09-11 1392
