for clients of the NYTimes News Service for AMs and PMs of Tuesday,
Sept. 12, and thereafter. If you have any questions, please call
Tom Uhler, Lou Hudson or Jim Peipert on the Star-Telegram's
National/Foreign Desk at (817) 390-7785. &QL; 
