   KENNEDY-ARREST (Undated) -- Joan B. Kennedy, former wife of US
Senator Edward M. Kennedy, is arrested for drunk driving. The
arrest is her fourth since 1974 and comes just as the 64-year-old
admitted alcoholic said that she had achieved some balance in life.
By Steven Wilmsen. 900 words.
</P>
<P>
   &UR; FINANCIAL (f) &LR;
