Renagel, a dialysis drug it shares with Geltex, and expands
Genzyme's product lines. By Ronald Rosenberg. 800 words.
</P>
<P>
   OLY-HANCOCK (Boston) _ John Hancock ad that ran during the US
Gymastics Trials was cheered for showcasing a lesbian couple with a
newly adopted baby. Now Hancock has completely reworked the ad --
because, it says, the focus was on the women's relationship, not
Hancock. By Chris Reidy. 700 words. (f and s coding)
</P>
