<P>
   LIQUID ASSETS: Next year's Senior PGA Tour stop at Golf Club of
Georgia in Alpharetta will have its own Internet connection.
LiquidGolf.com will be the title sponsor of the tournament Sept.
17-23, 2001. The online ``country club,'' which offers equipment,
instruction and help in finding courses and playing partners, also
will be the presenting sponsor of the Bank One Senior Championship
in Dallas, and national sponsor of the Ace Group Classic in Naples,
Fla.
</P>
