-- First lady Hillary Rodham Clinton, running for the U.S. Senate
seat from New York, gets a kiss from her husband, President Bill
Clinton, after she gave him a tour of her campaign van, Monday.
Clinton is in the region helping his wife on the campaign trail.
(James Estrin/The New York Times)
