CABLE: Jason Frankovitz figured it would be a breeze to sign up for
AT&AMP;T's superfast cable modem service. Frankovitz already has AT&AMP;T's
digital cable service. He lives in Berkeley, where AT&AMP;T has
upgraded its equipment to deliver both speedy Internet service and
local phone service. And AT&AMP;T mailed him a full-color brochure
promising to install the service within a week. But Frankovitz said
customer service representatives keep telling him he's out of luck.
The company can't serve some apartments because of a conflict with
landlords. BY TODD WALLACK. &QL; 
